text:
Hello all,

Hope you’re having a great week thus far!!

Quick pole for the 9 people who said they could hike this Sunday (plus Cherie)…
<@U03UM07E4D8> +1 (your husband?), <@U041PH0B1DF>, <@U8QDSG1G9> <@U042J1GTDRR> <@U04184BSKM3> <@U02UAQKR56C> <@U041TEG4UTC> <@U041RUTKBG9> <@U04263B0EMP> <@USASEN6LV>
(Will also assume there’s <@UMQUVR2VD> +1, and <@U02BQJX5TB8>)
(Maybe <@U013YD2ACLC> or just his dog)
-
For a total of *14 cool kids* for the hike
How concerned are you with the weather?

:+1: Will come, YOLO
:-1: Will not come, I am scared!!

*And the 7 people who want to eat* so I can try and make reservations if possible
--- vote on one only if possible to break ties:
:pancakes: Metro Cafe Diner (Diner food: <https://metrocafediner.com/stone-mountain-menu/> 1905 Rockbridge Rd, Stone Mountain, GA 30087-3310)- 9 minute drive from trail
:dumpling: Dim Sum Heaven  (5203 Buford Hwy NE, Doraville, GA 30340) - 20 minutes
:ramen: Food Terminal (Food Terminal, 5000 Buford Hwy NE, Chamblee, GA 30341) - 22 minutes
:takeout_box:  Yummy Spicy (<https://yummyspicygatogo.com/)-> 19-26 minutes
:sweat_smile: Fine with all places
:rage: I dislike all these places, but I’ll come watch people eat or message you for alternatives

Will assume there are a total of 7 students with a plus one. => *8 cool kids*

P.S. People that need cars are me (By Lenox mall) and <@U02BQJX5TB8> (in Midtown)
-Can <@U8QDSG1G9> (although you live by Marietta?) or <@UMQUVR2VD> sweep us up (You might be closest to N. Buckhead from Dunwoody)? || <@U041PH0B1DF> <@U04185JLG8M>

Thanks for always participating yall!!
I hope to see ya’ll again before it gets freezing!!!

Cherie Lum
